Title: Temporal Immunity
Description:
Zhusadormu has been trying hard to keep his powers in check.

While we may not be able to prevent his allergies, he does not have to jump through time with each sneeze.

Wurallie believes she can test his control. Please go to the Waking Shores and help them with this lesson.
ObjectivesText: Help Zhusadormu confront his allergies during a pet battle.
RewardText:
A sneeze without a teleport! A breakthrough to be proud of.

Now that he won't get lost, Zhusadormu will want to join you on some quests

Objectives.Text: Visit Wurallie in the Waking Shores
Defeat Wurallie in a Pet Battle with Annuna on your team
